column2: SELECT GN.objID, GN.distance,s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zErr, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian,zp.z, zp.zErr, stf.logmass FROM SpecObjAll as s  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS GN ON s.bestObjID = GN.objID   JOIN Photoz as zp ON zp.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort AS stf ON stf.specobjid = s.specobjid  WHERE s.class = &&& AND  s.zWarning=# AND s.z <=# ORDER BY distance
